OL,3,CTown to become one of first in country
OL,4,Cto forcibly lease out empty shops
OL,6,FA council is set to become one of the
OL,7,Ffirst in the country to unlock new
OL,8,Fpowers to lease out privately-owned
OL,9,Fshops left empty for too long.
OL,11,FRugby in Warwickshire has one of the
OL,12,Fworst shop vacancy rates in the
OL,13,Fcountry - with one in four sitting
OL,14,Fempty in June.
OL,16,FIn an attempt to revive the high
OL,17,Fstreet, the borough council will be
OL,18,Fable to tackle retail units in the
OL,19,Ftown centre that have been vacant for
OL,20,Fa year or more.
