OL,3,CTown to become one of first in country
OL,4,Cto forcibly lease out empty shops
OL,6,FThe council has compiled a list of
OL,7,Fempty shops, which will be updated
OL,8,Fmonthly and which is required by the
OL,9,Fgovernment to unlock the new 'High
OL,10,FStreet Rental Auctions' powers.
OL,12,FOfficers have also begun speaking with
OL,13,Flandowners of premises that need the
OL,14,Fmost work.
OL,16,FAs a "last resort", the council's
OL,17,Fchief executive will serve notices to
OL,18,Fbe able to lease out retail units, on
OL,19,Fbehalf of landlords. Landlords have
OL,20,Feight weeks to find a tenant, or can
OL,21,Ffight the council's decision.
