OL,3,CTown to become one of first in country
OL,4,Cto forcibly lease out empty shops
OL,6,FThere will be costs, like marketing
OL,7,Ffees and the cost of building surveys.
OL,8,FBut these should not exceed #5,223 and
OL,9,Fshould be covered by government grants
OL,10,Fin the first year, the council said.
OL,12,FThe government has allocated #1.5
OL,13,Fmillion to revamp commercial premises,
OL,14,Fand there is a 'New Burdens' grant for
OL,15,Flocal authorities.
OL,17,FBy the next financial year of 2026-27,
OL,18,Fthe council aims to have a budget to
OL,19,Fcover the costs of these High Street
OL,20,FRental Auctions.
