OL,3,CTown to become one of first in country
OL,4,Cto forcibly lease out empty shops
OL,6,FLeader Councillor Michael Moran (Lab,
OL,7,FAdmirals & Cawston) said: "It is great
OL,8,Fto see Rugby at the forefront of this
OL,9,Finitiative.
OL,11,F"Subject to confirmation we will be
OL,12,Fone of the first to adopt this, if not
OL,13,Fthe first, so we are at the cutting
OL,14,Fedge.
OL,16,F"There is huge technical detail to
OL,17,Fthis but what it amounts to is a
OL,18,Flegislative hammer to effectively
OL,19,Fattack empty properties and redundant
OL,20,Fshops.
